左係又一城出口售票處個位，好好彩有個男仔見到我縮埋左係一角，叫一叫我，發現我無意識。即刻搵地鐵站職員call左白車。<br />\n雖然唔知佢係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但真係好想處同佢講聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢好似係趕時間都幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵左職員，到職員拎輪椅都留係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />送到入地鐵休息室先離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝你一世平安健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港都係有好人好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cbeec7e11d4d86dd93eb44605071f67da4440c","tid":1085247,"uid":104075,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T17:21:04.000Z","msg":"幾年前同嗰時個男朋友嘈大交<br />\n自己一個人坐喺尖沙咀海旁喊到崩潰<br />\n有個陌生人買咗支水同紙巾 靜靜地放咗喺我張櫈側邊<br />\n我掛住喊所以冇抬頭望<br />\n淨係講咗句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗚嗚 多謝你呀<br />\n其實嗰下個心真係好溫暖 真係好多謝佢"},{"pid":"1d991bf1147a9951f919e682ee9ad797d2127ac0","tid":1085247,"uid":